Package: LaplaceMeasure
Title: Modeling Measurement Errors with Laplace Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: oumeguelejunior
Maintainer: <oumeguelejunior@gmail.com>
Description: Implements statistical methods for modeling measurement errors using 
    Laplace distribution. Provides maximum likelihood estimation, uncertainty 
    quantification, and confidence intervals for measurement error analysis.
